parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag control unit can cause the airbag warning light to illuminate, indicating a potential failure of the airbag system, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a collision.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag indicator light stays on continuously
warnings lights turn on and won't turn off
the airbag may not deploy in case of a collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to receive recall notification can prevent vehicle owners from being aware of potential safety issues and taking necessary steps to have them repaired, which can increase the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Vehicle owners do not receive recall notification letters
manufacturers refuse to send additional recall letters.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank assembly can cause gasoline leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, and accidents, posing a significant risk to vehicle occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Gasoline leaks from the fuel tank
fuel smell inside or outside the vehicle
decreased fuel efficiency
fuel gauge fluctuations.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank ventilation system can cause fuel vapors to escape, leading to a potential fire hazard, and restrict the amount of fuel that can be filled, resulting in reduced fuel efficiency and increased fuel costs.
symptoms: Fuel vapors appear when filling up the vehicle
unable to fill the tank completely
only able to get a half tank of gas
fuel tank takes a long time to fill
fuel pump shuts off prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The restriction in fuel tank capacity can cause inconvenience, reduced fuel efficiency, and increased fuel costs.
symptoms: Unable to fill the tank completely
only able to get a half tank of gas
fuel tank takes a long time to fill
fuel pump shuts off prematurely.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distraction while driving, leading to accidents, and can also result in the loss of important features such as navigation and Bluetooth connectivity.
symptoms: The radio or infotainment system freezes or locks up
the screen is unresponsive
the system fails to turn on
the system randomly restarts
the system displays error messages.
